data.description: This charming 3-bedroom home is situated in the Fortune Hills neighborhood, which offers community ponds and a playground. It provides the perfect balance, offering easy access to Ambassador Caffery and the convenience of shopping and dining options in Youngsville.The home features impressive 12-foot ceilings in the living, dining, and kitchen areas, adorned with beautiful wood flooring and an abundance of windows that flood the space with natural light. The kitchen is both airy and inviting, featuring granite countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, including a gas range, and a spacious eat-in island that is ideal for gatherings. The primary bedroom is generously sized and comes with an attached bathroom that includes a double sink vanity, a relaxing garden tub, a separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Additionally, the covered patio has an attractive tongue and groove wood ceiling, offering lovely views of the fully fenced backyard
